com.swirl

Class SObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swirl.SObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Config.BeaconConfiguration, Config.Firmware, Config.Floorplan, Config.Partner, Config.User, Location, Placement, Signal

    public class SObject
extends java.lang.Object
    SObject is the base class for all Swirl platform objects. Object contains the JSON data of all object properties and defines accessors for identifier and name.
